Édition de 1899</td>
<td width="33%" style="text-align:right;font-size:90%;"><a href="/wiki/Bible_du_Rabbinat_1899/Jo%C3%ABl" title="Bible du Rabbinat 1899/Joël">Joël</a><span class="%5B%5BBible+du+Rabbinat+1899%2FJo%C3%ABl%7CJo%C3%ABl%5D%5DhiddenStructure" style="color:#808080">&#160;&#160;►</span></td>
